{"tid":2055700,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"床蝨治理方法","createTime":"2020-06-08T07:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T19:17:40.000Z","uid":38861,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"defa78f3a10190b5b06597eac978e0850bd754c7","tid":2055700,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1905840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMcp1905840&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3115446f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMcp1905840</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHKhiRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHKhiRO.jpg&h=0bb329fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n床蝨不懂跳及飛，每分鐘約可步行100cm左右。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普遍殺蟲水均沒法殺死牠們，但牠們及其產卵在攝氏60度一分鐘的處理過後便會完全被消滅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於牠們孵化的平均日子為5-12日，床單各用品應在每五日後用高溫作清洗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP1jxbN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP1jxbN.png&h=5d2d30b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用燙斗處理的話，速度平均每秒3cm ，50度以上，入布料內部1.1-1.8cm。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533c0678f1dfe7fc643e12e864d2c6da5b989c85","tid":2055700,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"熱死班仆街就啱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f851cc08bd3081c5e80ca9a2b0d39aaa68a6f360","tid":2055700,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"533c0678f1dfe7fc643e12e864d2c6da5b989c85","tid":2055700,"uid":34422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"熱死班仆街就啱架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者燙死佢及吸走佢"},{"pid":"54787bf0f40a1430f1ad68bc42ded006cf24afb6","tid":2055700,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"屌我果張床單五年無洗過..."},{"pid":"93f382c3a55cce7bf58afa584ce86fc7c6a6b309","tid":2055700,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"之前試過用De粉，灑係床邊，之後Keep住見到有屍，死下死下就清左"},{"pid":"f2b74bc69475a476b16103a35c418f3bb42eaa97","tid":2055700,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54787bf0f40a1430f1ad68bc42ded006cf24afb6","tid":2055700,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"屌我果張床單五年無洗過..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"一定好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59697aad9fad7a3bf4be9e784e249bb66a96463","tid":2055700,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b74bc69475a476b16103a35c418f3bb42eaa97","tid":2055700,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54787bf0f40a1430f1ad68bc42ded006cf24afb6","tid":2055700,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"屌我果張床單五年無洗過..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"一定好撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"如果數量非常多的話，啲床蝨好似會釋放類近櫻桃的氣味......."},{"pid":"fb474be158695f5cd03a31eb1f022e30079e13a2","tid":2055700,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c59697aad9fad7a3bf4be9e784e249bb66a96463","tid":2055700,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b74bc69475a476b16103a35c418f3bb42eaa97","tid":2055700,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54787bf0f40a1430f1ad68bc42ded006cf24afb6","tid":2055700,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20